PN,35301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,FMore than 12,000 people have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition urging an energy firm to
OL,8,Fcancel plans to build an offshore wind
OL,9,Ffarm.
OL,11,FNature charities supported the
OL,12,Fpetition, which hopes to stop the
OL,13,Fdevelopment of Berwick Bank, which
OL,14,Fcould see more than 300 turbines
OL,15,Fcovering 1,000 square kilometres off
OL,16,Fthe East Lothian coast.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,FCampaigners, including the Scottish
OL,7,FWildlife Trust, RSPB and Scottish
OL,8,FSeabird Centre, say the proposals
OL,9,Fwould endanger the lives of seabirds -
OL,10,Fsuch as puffins and guillemots -
OL,11,Faround the wind farm.
OL,13,FIf built the Berwick Bank wind farm
OL,14,Fwould be the largest in the world.
OL,16,FThe plans from Perth-based energy firm
OL,17,FSSE Renewables were approved by the
OL,18,FScottish Government in July 2025, on
OL,19,Fthe condition that a 'sufficient
OL,20,Fseabird compensation plan' is put in
OL,21,Fplace.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,FCampaigners gathered outside of SSE
OL,7,Fheadquarters to express their
OL,8,Fopposition to the proposals.
OL,10,FAnne McCall, Director of RSPB
OL,11,FScotland, said: "We joined the
OL,12,Fdemonstration with the simple message:
OL,13,Fstop Berwick Bank. Scotland's
OL,14,Fincredible seabirds are in crisis, and
OL,15,Fclimate change is one of the many
OL,16,Fthreats they face.
OL,18,F"Berwick Bank is planned in the worst
OL,19,Fpossible place, close to
OL,20,Finternationally important seabird
OL,21,Fsites like the Bass Rock.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,F"It would sit slap bang in the middle
OL,7,Fof a vital area where puffins, gannets
OL,8,Fand guillemots search for food for
OL,9,Ftheir chicks."
OL,11,FHarry Huyton, CEO of the Scottish
OL,12,FSeabird Centre said: "We are grateful
OL,13,Fto the 12,000 plus nature lovers who
OL,14,Fare sending SSE a stark message today
OL,15,F` the potential impacts of Berwick
OL,16,FBank are too devastating for it to go
OL,17,Fforward as proposed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,F"We want to see a thriving offshore
OL,7,Fwind industry that is helping Scotland
OL,8,Fmeet its climate goals and build a
OL,9,Fgreen economy, but it must be
OL,10,Fdeveloped in harmony with nature."
OL,12,FJo Pike, CEO of the Scottish Wildlife
OL,13,FTrust said: "The amazing response to
OL,14,Fthe petition mirrors the strength of
OL,15,Ffeeling we have heard from our members
OL,16,Fand the communities we work with, both
OL,17,Fin Berwickshire and across Scotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,F"They are disappointed and shocked
OL,7,Fthat this development has been granted
OL,8,Fconsent, given the implications for
OL,9,Four seabird populations.
OL,11,F"It is clear that renewable energy is
OL,12,Fneeded in our response to the climate
OL,13,Fcrisis, but there are ways of
OL,14,Fexpanding offshore wind without the
OL,15,Fdevastating impacts that Berwick Bank
OL,16,Fwould have. We do not believe there is
OL,17,Fa way to compensate for these impacts."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,FIn response, SSE Renewables said:
OL,7,F"Berwick Bank is a worldleading
OL,8,Frenewable energy project, not just in
OL,9,Fits scale but in its careful design
OL,10,Fand potential to tackle climate
OL,11,Fchange. It is shaped by more than a
OL,12,Fdecade of meticulous development and
OL,13,Fplanning and reflects our commitment
OL,14,Fto environmental responsibility.
OL,16,F"With consent now granted, we are
OL,17,Frefining seabird compensation measures
OL,18,Ffor submission to the Scottish
OL,19,FGovernment later this year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
