PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773504677
OL,3,C12,000 sign petition to stop offshore
OL,4,Cwind farm
OL,6,F"We will continue to work
OL,7,Fconstructively with environmental
OL,8,Fstakeholders including RSPB and other
OL,9,Fconservation bodies throughout this
OL,10,Fprocess.:
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/8
